GRID-Machine version 0.07
=========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

Optionally, if you want to thoroughly test the module do this two steps:

  - Set automatic ssh-authentification with a machine where you have an account
  - Set on the local machine the environment variable GRID_REMOTE_MACHINE to point
    to taht machine. For example:

        export GRID_REMOTE_MACHINE=user@machine.domain

Then follow these steps:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Module::Which version '0.0205'

